\right)=\frac{h\cos{\theta}}{\lambda},
\end{align*}
which simplifies to
\begin{equation}
T_e=(mc^2)\left[
\frac{1-(1-\beta)^2}{1+(1-\beta)^2+2(1-\beta)\cos{\theta}}
